'''[[empty]] [[sum]]''' (''plural'' '''empty sums''')

#{{arithmetic}} The result of [[add]]ing no numbers (defined in order to be able to extend certain mathematical concepts, such as the sum of ''n'' numbers, to the case where ''n'' = 0).

